CHINA GLAZE CO said unconsolidated sales
in April rose 8.61% to NT$151,223,000 from NT$139,231,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            151,223          139,231    
YOY%              8.61%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            557,565          473,120    
YOY%              17.85% 
=================================================================
 